<item>
            <title>[SPARK-4837] NettyBlockTransferService does not abide by spark.blockManager.port config option</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-4837</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The NettyBlockTransferService always binds to a random port, and does not use the spark.blockManager.port config as specified.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12761535">SPARK-4837</key>
